description: Therapy is your therapist for Alexa.  Tell therapist how you are feeling and she will give you some words of encouragements.  Therapy is a lighthearted skill that tries to make your day a little better.  Over 500 new moods and words of encouragement!
exampleInteractions: Alexa, tell My Therapist I am excited.
Alexa, tell My Therapist I feel sad.
Alexa, tell My Therapist i am feeling happy.
name: Therapy
shortDescription: Therapy is your therapist for Alexa.  Tell therapist your mood and she will give you words of encouragements.  Alexa, tell my therapist I am excited.
